1
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:51,680
A relative of the Emperor is indeed special.

2
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:54,360
After committing a mistake, he is allowed to attend the offering ceremony.

3
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:55,160
Hailancha.

4
00:02:55,720 --> 00:02:56,760
By the way,

5
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:59,130
you're also a relative of His Majesty,

6
00:02:59,160 --> 00:03:01,360
but you don't have those stinky traits of Hongxiao.

7
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:02,240
It shows

8
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:04,560
that the noble title of "Prince Yi”

9
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:05,960
isn't anything special.

10
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:08,900
Don’t gossip in chitchat.

11
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:15,640
What happened?

12
00:03:16,280 --> 00:03:17,360
He’s in such a rush.

13
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:28,050
Your Majesty...

14
00:03:40,320 --> 00:03:41,250
Investigate it.

15
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:42,240
Yes.

16
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:56,170
What's going on?

17
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:38,480
Your Majesty, we found it.

18
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:53,280
Hongxiao,

19
00:04:55,080 --> 00:04:58,120
why does the Qing dynasty share the blessings by eating meat?

20
00:04:58,120 --> 00:04:59,240
Do you remember it?

21
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:01,400
I do.

22
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:04,240
Emperor Taizu had to be separated from his family at a young age.

23
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:06,960
He brought his brothers into the mountain to pick ginseng and hunt.

24
00:05:06,960 --> 00:05:09,080
They survived by cooking meat in boiling water.

25
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:10,720
Afterwards, we maintained this tradition.

26
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:12,440
After our ancestors crossed Shanhaiguan,

27
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:14,760
Palace of Earthly Tranquility holds offering ceremonies in the morning and at night,

28
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:16,000
and one major offering ceremony every three months.

29
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:17,680
This is to help the Qing descendants

30
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:19,920
remember the hardships of our ancestors

31
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:21,720
in establishing a great undertaking.

32
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:23,120
Since you know it,

33
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:26,200
why did you add salt to the meat?

34
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:29,080
Add salt?

35
00:05:30,400 --> 00:05:31,520
I didn't!

36
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:32,720
Taste it yourself.

37
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:47,850
Our ancestors could endure it,

38
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:50,680
and you can’t.

39
00:05:51,240 --> 00:05:53,040
Adding salt to sacrificial meat

40
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:55,600
is clearly disrespectful to our ancestors

41
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:56,800
and the gods.

42
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:58,720
You are too bold!

43
00:05:59,200 --> 00:05:59,920
Somebody!

44
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:03,960
Prince Yi disrespected the ancestors and tainted the sacrificial meat.

45
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:07,620
His position as a Guard of the Gate of Celestial Purity is revoked.

46
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:09,360
Hand him to the Imperial Clan Court

47
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:11,160
Your Majesty, Your Majesty, I didn't!

48
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:11,960
Your Majesty,

49
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:14,040
I didn't bring any salt into the Palace!

50
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:15,560
Your Majesty, I'm innocent.

51
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:16,360
Your Majesty,

52
00:06:16,880 --> 00:06:17,680
Your Majesty,

53
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:19,520
I’m innocent.

54
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:30,780
Doing offering ceremonies day and night, sharing the sacrificial meat,

55
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:34,640
these are blessings from our ancestors,

56
00:06:34,640 --> 00:06:36,300
and protection from the gods.

57
00:06:37,960 --> 00:06:40,420
But those descendants of the eight banners,

58
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:43,080
headed by Prince Yi,

59
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:47,680
who were previously valiant and skillful in warfare,

60
00:06:47,960 --> 00:06:49,800
are now insects that rely on their ancestors' merits.

61
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:51,930
They just play with birds or walk dogs.

62
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,600
Not to say fighting enemies,

63
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,880
eating sacrificial meat

64
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:59,420
is already a hard task to them.

65
00:07:05,400 --> 00:07:06,960
I have to warn all of you.

66
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:12,000
The establishment of the Qing Dynasty wasn’t easy.

67
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:13,640
I will never allow

68
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:15,040
this great empire

69
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:17,960
to get destroyed in the hands of a group of prodigal sons

70
00:07:17,960 --> 00:07:22,090
who only know how to seek pleasure and are disrespectful to our ancestors!

71
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:24,960
Investigate!

72
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:29,140
Investigate the guards outside too!

73
00:07:30,440 --> 00:07:32,880
I want to look clearly who else

74
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:35,010
dares to do such a thing!

75
00:07:35,159 --> 00:07:35,920
Yes.

76
00:07:49,400 --> 00:07:50,080
Start.

77
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:57,360
Isn’t it ridiculous?

78
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:58,960
When are you servants

79
00:07:58,960 --> 00:07:59,800
allowed to investigate us?

80
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:00,480
Hailancha.

81
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,570
Lords, sorry to offend you.

82
00:08:06,360 --> 00:08:07,160
Start.

83
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:15,040
Master Fuheng, please.

84
00:08:39,640 --> 00:08:40,440
Your Majesty.

85
00:08:41,520 --> 00:08:42,520
Did you catch any?

86
00:08:42,909 --> 00:08:44,800
The imperial bodyguards and guards of the Gate of Celestial Purity

87
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:46,480
have all been checked.

88
00:08:46,560 --> 00:08:48,890
No one else is found to have played a trick.

89
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:55,820
Fortunately there are sensible people.

90
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:59,000
Continue to eat the meat.

91
00:08:59,000 --> 00:08:59,680
Yes.

92
00:09:04,760 --> 00:09:07,320
May all lords continue to eat the meat.

93
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:14,480
Why wasn’t Fuheng caught?

94
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:25,120
Young Master,

95
00:09:26,280 --> 00:09:27,210
are you alright?

96
00:09:29,800 --> 00:09:31,360
I was so scared.

97
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:34,520
Prince Yi got demoted and sent for investigation

98
00:09:34,520 --> 00:09:35,980
just for hiding some salt.

99
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:38,480
He was even sent to the Imperial Clan Court.

100
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:39,840
If I've known it earlier,

101
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:42,700
I shouldn't have told you to bring that spiced salt.

102
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:45,480
Good thing you didn't bring it today.

103
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:02,640
So

104
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:05,490
you noticed it beforehand.

105
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:08,160
You told on Prince Yi?

106
00:10:08,160 --> 00:10:08,800
Yes.

107
00:10:09,920 --> 00:10:10,480
You...

108
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:11,880
I what?

109
00:10:12,400 --> 00:10:15,120
Are you going to tell me that I shouldn't have told on him

110
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:17,450
because he's a prince of the Qing Dynasty,

111
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:20,480
a descendant of the royal family, and has a noble status?

112
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:22,680
So when he told me to kneel, I must kneel.

113
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:24,680
When he called me bitch, I just have to accept all that.

114
00:10:24,680 --> 00:10:25,480
Is that so?

115
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:26,320
Listen now.

116
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,840
I indeed came from a lowly family,

117
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:30,570
but I won't let anyone bully me.

118
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:32,840
He is a prince, after all.

119
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:35,640
Things in this world change.

120
00:10:36,280 --> 00:10:37,680
Peaking mountain ridges

121
00:10:38,160 --> 00:10:40,400
might become a boundless plain in the future.

122
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:43,060
Change is the only constant thing in this world.

123
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:45,820
You seek vengeance for the smallest grudge,

124
00:10:46,240 --> 00:10:47,900
and are extremely audacious.

125
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:49,840
I just wanted to give him a lesson.

126
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:50,700
I'm telling him

127
00:10:51,160 --> 00:10:53,400
that an ant can shake an elephant.

128
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:55,360
Any bully

129
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:59,600
will eventually get bullied.

130
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:00,880
What about me?

131
00:11:04,160 --> 00:11:05,440
You escaped

132
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:09,000
because you were doubtful of me?

133
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:09,680
No.

134
00:11:11,040 --> 00:11:14,370
I just didn’t want to disobey the teachings of my ancestors.

135
00:11:16,040 --> 00:11:17,770
So I threw away the spiced salt.

136
00:11:18,560 --> 00:11:19,560
On the outside,

137
00:11:21,680 --> 00:11:23,400
you are indeed a gentleman.

138
00:11:26,040 --> 00:11:28,970
But how could a gentleman ruin the chastity of a girl?

139
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:32,010
You repeatedly schemed against me

140
00:11:32,440 --> 00:11:34,440
because of Ah-Man, right?

141
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,160
Yes.

142
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,080
If I tell you

143
00:11:40,560 --> 00:11:41,620
that I didn't do it,

144
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:43,120
will you believe me?

145
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,240
You think I will?

146
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:55,650
I can swear by the heaven

147
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:58,440
that this matter had nothing to do with me.

148
00:11:58,440 --> 00:11:59,770
If you don't believe me,

149
00:12:01,760 --> 00:12:02,920
you can kill me now.

150
00:12:04,920 --> 00:12:05,800
You think I wouldn't dare!

151
00:12:05,800 --> 00:12:06,520
You would.

152
00:12:07,880 --> 00:12:10,440
Is there anything in this world that you won't dare do?

153
00:12:10,440 --> 00:12:11,880
But no is no.

154
00:12:12,840 --> 00:12:14,300
I didn't hurt your sister.

155
00:12:15,320 --> 00:12:16,640
I didn't hurt Ah-Man.

156
00:12:17,160 --> 00:12:18,490
If you don't believe me,

157
00:12:19,160 --> 00:12:20,640
you can use this dagger

158
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:22,680
to stab my chest.

159
00:12:34,680 --> 00:12:35,360
Yingluo,

160
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,130
I'm saying it again.

161
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:41,160
I would never do anything offensive to god or conscience.

162
00:12:41,160 --> 00:12:42,120
I never have.

163
00:13:13,760 --> 00:13:14,520
Sister,

164
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:18,160
sorry.

165
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:22,000
I wasn't able to kill him.

166
00:13:26,560 --> 00:13:28,360
But this is the Imperial Palace.

167
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:30,400
If I really kill someone,

168
00:13:30,840 --> 00:13:32,040
what about father?

169
00:13:34,160 --> 00:13:35,160
Even so,

170
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:38,500
I've already committed a grave mistake.

171
00:13:39,600 --> 00:13:42,860
I can't continue staying here in Palace of Eternal Spring.

172
00:13:49,440 --> 00:13:51,040
Her Majesty wants to see you.

173
00:13:52,840 --> 00:13:53,760
I knew it.

174
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:57,240
You will eventually fall and get smashed into pieces.

175
00:14:00,280 --> 00:14:01,040
Wei Yingluo,

176
00:14:01,520 --> 00:14:02,850
do you admit your fault?

177
00:14:06,560 --> 00:14:07,320
Yingluo,

178
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:10,810
Her Majesty rarely gets angry.

179
00:14:11,120 --> 00:14:12,320
Tell her the truth.

180
00:14:13,680 --> 00:14:15,440
It's already too late to admit it.

181
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:16,760
After committing such a grave mistake,

182
00:14:16,760 --> 00:14:18,220
just wait to get beheaded!

183
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:21,680
It was my own doing

184
00:14:21,880 --> 00:14:23,680
and didn't involve anyone else.

185
00:14:24,440 --> 00:14:27,920
I earnestly ask Your Majesty to just punish me.

186
00:14:28,680 --> 00:14:29,920
You, oh, you!

187
00:14:30,920 --> 00:14:32,960
Did you eat something bold, maybe a bear?

188
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:34,620
How come you are not fat at all?

189
00:14:35,400 --> 00:14:36,260
Stop laughing.

190
00:14:38,360 --> 00:14:40,640
You can't see Yingluo suffer.

191
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:43,160
She exposed the wrongdoings of Prince Yi,

192
00:14:43,160 --> 00:14:44,960
but you can't bear to punish her.

193
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:48,100
When Prince Yi framed Yingluo last time,

194
00:14:48,160 --> 00:14:50,240
he was slapping our Palace of Eternal Spring.

195
00:14:50,240 --> 00:14:52,000
Of course, I'm unhappy with him.

196
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:54,130
I also hoped that he could be punished.

197
00:14:54,480 --> 00:14:57,360
But he's after all a cousin of His Majesty.

198
00:14:57,760 --> 00:15:00,760
If His Majesty doesn't allow it, I can't castigate him.

199
00:15:00,760 --> 00:15:02,320
But this person is so bold!

200
00:15:03,040 --> 00:15:04,840
You even dared touch a prince!

201
00:15:07,560 --> 00:15:09,160
Your Majesty is scolding me

202
00:15:09,880 --> 00:15:11,480
just for this?

203
00:15:13,000 --> 00:15:14,400
Is there anything else?

204
00:15:16,280 --> 00:15:18,520
Did Fuheng not tell Her Majesty?

205
00:15:18,800 --> 00:15:20,000
How is this possible?

206
00:15:21,920 --> 00:15:23,400
You're really something, Wei Yingluo.

207
00:15:23,400 --> 00:15:25,460
What else did you do? Quickly tell me,

208
00:15:25,640 --> 00:15:27,500
so that I won't get shocked again!

209
00:15:28,400 --> 00:15:29,930
How did you know about this?

210
00:15:30,200 --> 00:15:31,440
How did I know?

211
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:34,330
Fuheng wrote me a letter

212
00:15:34,600 --> 00:15:36,280
saying that you were extremely audacious

213
00:15:36,280 --> 00:15:38,010
and asked me to discipline you.

214
00:15:38,280 --> 00:15:40,140
Isn't he doing this for your good?

215
00:15:40,160 --> 00:15:42,480
Or else, don't know what other troubles you would start.

216
00:15:42,480 --> 00:15:44,540
Guard Fuca didn't say anything else?

217
00:15:45,400 --> 00:15:46,680
Who is Imperial Guard Fuca?

218
00:15:46,680 --> 00:15:48,960
You think he has the time to care about you?

219
00:15:48,960 --> 00:15:52,200
His Majesty might be happy to see it.

220
00:15:54,120 --> 00:15:55,280
What do you mean?

221
00:15:55,840 --> 00:15:57,880
High officials have disliked the sacrificial meat

222
00:15:57,880 --> 00:15:59,240
and employed tricks to eat it

223
00:15:59,240 --> 00:16:00,360
for a long time.

224
00:16:01,640 --> 00:16:04,400
His Majesty used the incident of punishing Prince Yi

225
00:16:04,400 --> 00:16:06,400
to warn others from following suit.

226
00:16:06,600 --> 00:16:08,930
Or else, he could have just denounced him.

227
00:16:09,120 --> 00:16:11,720
Why must he send him to the Imperial Clan Court?

228
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:16,320
Wei Yingluo!

229
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:18,960
Even if what you said is true,

230
00:16:19,360 --> 00:16:21,960
if you are too particular about every detail in everything,

231
00:16:21,960 --> 00:16:23,820
you won't be able to live happily.

232
00:16:24,320 --> 00:16:28,120
Take a step back and you'll be able to appreciate how vast the world is.

233
00:16:28,120 --> 00:16:30,320
I'm punishing you to write the word "forgiveness"

234
00:16:30,320 --> 00:16:31,240
100 times!

235
00:16:32,560 --> 00:16:33,360
Your Majesty,

236
00:16:33,600 --> 00:16:34,860
she is this audacious,

237
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:36,810
and you're going to let her off?

238
00:16:38,480 --> 00:16:40,480
I just taught her to take a step back.

239
00:16:41,520 --> 00:16:44,000
Now, if I punish her harshly,

240
00:16:44,560 --> 00:16:46,160
isn't that going against what I said?

241
00:16:46,160 --> 00:16:48,320
You keep being biased to her, and harboring her!

242
00:16:48,320 --> 00:16:49,000
Mingyu.

243
00:16:53,040 --> 00:16:54,680
What happened here today

244
00:16:55,160 --> 00:16:56,880
is known to only the four of us.

245
00:16:57,800 --> 00:16:59,960
No one can leak it.

246
00:17:00,440 --> 00:17:01,040
Remember.

247
00:17:01,880 --> 00:17:03,480
It must not be disclosed.

248
00:17:04,109 --> 00:17:05,040
Or else,

249
00:17:05,800 --> 00:17:07,460
I will not easily forgive you.

250
00:17:07,800 --> 00:17:08,560
Yes.

251
00:17:09,720 --> 00:17:10,480
Yes.

252
00:17:13,520 --> 00:17:14,440
Go now.

253
00:17:14,960 --> 00:17:15,560
Yes.

254
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:20,640
Wait.

255
00:17:22,880 --> 00:17:24,740
May Your Majesty give your order.

256
00:17:25,520 --> 00:17:27,640
Fuheng was injured when he was practicing martial-arts.

257
00:17:27,640 --> 00:17:28,640
I'm very worried.

258
00:17:29,320 --> 00:17:31,580
Help me deliver some ginseng soup to him.

259
00:17:31,880 --> 00:17:33,760
Your Majesty, let me do it.

260
00:17:33,880 --> 00:17:34,640
You?

261
00:17:35,080 --> 00:17:37,240
If you go, you won't be back in two hours.

262
00:17:37,240 --> 00:17:39,170
You'll be embarrassing yourself.

263
00:17:39,640 --> 00:17:40,570
Yingluo, you go.

264
00:17:40,920 --> 00:17:42,000
Come back quickly.

265
00:17:42,600 --> 00:17:43,360
Yes.

266
00:17:47,680 --> 00:17:50,610
You said that you got hurt on the martial-arts arena?

267
00:17:50,640 --> 00:17:52,000
How come I didn't know that?

268
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:54,760
I was accidentally hurt during a dueling practice.

269
00:17:54,760 --> 00:17:57,120
You've been nagging for so long. Aren't you tired?

270
00:17:57,120 --> 00:17:57,980
Can't be right.

271
00:17:58,760 --> 00:18:00,490
You are an imperial bodyguard.

272
00:18:01,040 --> 00:18:02,720
Could any guard of the Gate of Celestial Purity

273
00:18:02,720 --> 00:18:03,960
hurt you?

274
00:18:04,800 --> 00:18:06,530
Unless he used a sinister move.

275
00:18:06,840 --> 00:18:07,880
Tell me who it was.

276
00:18:07,960 --> 00:18:09,290
I'll handle him for you.

277
00:18:09,320 --> 00:18:10,680
I must admit defeat for bet.

278
00:18:10,680 --> 00:18:12,610
This is my business. Stay out of it.

279
00:18:13,960 --> 00:18:14,880
Ungrateful!

280
00:18:18,760 --> 00:18:19,600
Miss Yingluo.

281
00:18:20,960 --> 00:18:22,220
What brought you here?

282
00:18:27,880 --> 00:18:31,010
Her Majesty ordered me to deliver you some ginseng soup.

283
00:18:31,800 --> 00:18:33,060
Now I've delivered it,

284
00:18:33,360 --> 00:18:34,420
I'll take my leave.

285
00:18:35,360 --> 00:18:36,160
Miss Yingluo,

286
00:18:36,960 --> 00:18:38,520
didn't Her Majesty instruct you

287
00:18:38,520 --> 00:18:39,580
to do other things?

288
00:18:40,240 --> 00:18:40,920
What?

289
00:18:41,440 --> 00:18:42,800
Of course it's to express sympathy

290
00:18:42,800 --> 00:18:44,440
to the injured guard Fuca.

291
00:18:52,080 --> 00:18:53,680
I'll leave you alone. Alone.

292
00:19:04,120 --> 00:19:05,850
Why didn't you tell Her Majesty

293
00:19:06,040 --> 00:19:07,000
that I hurt you?

294
00:19:12,600 --> 00:19:13,800
I didn't hurt Ah-Man.

295
00:19:14,280 --> 00:19:15,840
Since my conscience is clear,

296
00:19:15,840 --> 00:19:17,520
the truth will come out sooner or later.

297
00:19:17,520 --> 00:19:19,050
You think that small favors

298
00:19:20,360 --> 00:19:21,520
can win my belief?

299
00:19:23,320 --> 00:19:24,080
Listen,

300
00:19:24,720 --> 00:19:26,400
I'm a stone-hearted person.

301
00:19:27,320 --> 00:19:30,440
I will never believe just because of a few words.

302
00:19:31,400 --> 00:19:33,680
Yingluo, let me say it again.

303
00:19:34,240 --> 00:19:35,720
I never hurt your sister.

304
00:19:35,920 --> 00:19:37,120
And I don't want to...

305
00:19:39,720 --> 00:19:41,050
I don't want to hurt you.

306
00:19:43,160 --> 00:19:45,200
When I asked you the first time

307
00:19:45,920 --> 00:19:47,250
that if you knew Ah-Man,

308
00:19:48,240 --> 00:19:50,170
why did you pretend not to know her?

309
00:19:52,000 --> 00:19:52,800
Ah-Man's case

310
00:19:53,760 --> 00:19:56,000
caused quite a stir in the Forbidden City.

311
00:19:56,000 --> 00:19:57,730
Even after she left the palace,

312
00:19:57,920 --> 00:19:59,850
the rumors didn't easily die down.

313
00:20:01,000 --> 00:20:02,460
I heard about this matter,

314
00:20:02,920 --> 00:20:04,400
but I have never seen her.

315
00:20:04,840 --> 00:20:06,800
Of course, I would say that I didn't know her.

316
00:20:06,800 --> 00:20:09,400
Why did she have your jade pendant?

317
00:20:12,280 --> 00:20:14,600
I lost that jade pendant.

318
00:20:15,600 --> 00:20:17,400
But as to why it ended up with her,

319
00:20:17,600 --> 00:20:18,480
I don't know.

320
00:20:22,160 --> 00:20:23,440
Does every word

321
00:20:25,280 --> 00:20:26,940
come from your sincere heart,

322
00:20:28,440 --> 00:20:29,760
and none is false?

323
00:20:30,080 --> 00:20:31,810
There's no need to deceive you.

324
00:20:32,280 --> 00:20:33,680
If I was the murderer,

325
00:20:34,280 --> 00:20:35,810
I can tell it to Her Majesty.

326
00:20:36,400 --> 00:20:39,200
You think you'd have the chance to seek vengeance?

327
00:20:41,360 --> 00:20:42,080
Ok.

328
00:20:43,520 --> 00:20:45,250
I'll temporarily believe you.

329
00:20:46,840 --> 00:20:47,640
If one day,

330
00:20:48,360 --> 00:20:49,820
I learn that you're lying,

331
00:20:50,400 --> 00:20:54,000
you’ll pay with your life even if I have turned into an evil ghost.

332
00:20:55,000 --> 00:20:55,720
Wait!

333
00:20:57,440 --> 00:20:58,640
What else do you need?

334
00:20:59,120 --> 00:21:00,760
When you were seeking vengeance on me,

335
00:21:00,760 --> 00:21:02,960
you were always courteous and smiling.

336
00:21:03,480 --> 00:21:05,120
Now you think I'm useless,

337
00:21:05,240 --> 00:21:06,840
you immediately disdain to care about me.

338
00:21:06,840 --> 00:21:09,120
Yingluo, are you a face changer?

339
00:21:13,040 --> 00:21:14,200
I suspected you

340
00:21:15,280 --> 00:21:16,540
after your first move.

341
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:18,760
After that,

342
00:21:18,800 --> 00:21:20,930
I saw your kindness towards Snowball.

343
00:21:22,000 --> 00:21:23,530
I then fooled myself again.

344
00:21:25,720 --> 00:21:26,400
Yingluo,

345
00:21:26,960 --> 00:21:28,840
it has never been you who has deceived me.

346
00:21:28,840 --> 00:21:31,040
It was I who have been deceiving myself.

347
00:21:33,760 --> 00:21:34,560
Young Master,

348
00:21:37,080 --> 00:21:37,880
sorry

349
00:21:39,200 --> 00:21:40,060
that I hurt you.

350
00:21:40,240 --> 00:21:41,700
I don't accept apologies.

351
00:21:42,760 --> 00:21:43,560
I only accept

352
00:21:44,400 --> 00:21:45,360
action.

353
00:21:51,600 --> 00:21:54,260
Didn't Her Majesty order you to deliver me soup?

354
00:22:05,360 --> 00:22:06,280
I'm injured.

355
00:22:09,880 --> 00:22:10,600
So?

356
00:22:10,800 --> 00:22:12,120
My chest is injured.

357
00:22:12,760 --> 00:22:15,720
The imperial doctor said that I must lie in bed for recuperation.

358
00:22:15,720 --> 00:22:17,050
I can't even lift my arm.

359
00:22:18,200 --> 00:22:21,280
May I ask Miss Yingluo to condescend and take care of me?

360
00:22:21,760 --> 00:22:23,020
You want me to feed you?

361
00:22:24,200 --> 00:22:27,060
That is the right attitude to take care of a patient.

362
00:22:27,720 --> 00:22:30,780
And the right attitude to apologize for one's mistake.

363
00:22:47,040 --> 00:22:47,720
It's hot.

364
00:23:01,800 --> 00:23:02,560
Yingluo,

365
00:23:04,160 --> 00:23:05,890
I've been recalling in my mind.

366
00:23:07,120 --> 00:23:08,780
every word that you said to me,

367
00:23:09,960 --> 00:23:11,840
and every smile you showed me.

368
00:23:15,280 --> 00:23:17,960
Even though I knew that you were lying,

369
00:23:19,960 --> 00:23:21,290
I refused to believe it.

370
00:23:26,120 --> 00:23:26,960
Tell me,

371
00:23:28,720 --> 00:23:31,360
you stabbed only a tenth of the dagger into my chest

372
00:23:31,360 --> 00:23:34,760
because you were worried of getting in trouble if you kill me,

373
00:23:36,640 --> 00:23:39,700
or because you also have a bit of sincere feeling for me?

374
00:23:48,920 --> 00:23:49,720
Young Master,

375
00:23:50,920 --> 00:23:52,160
your current action

376
00:23:53,120 --> 00:23:54,450
is a bit inappropriate.

377
00:23:58,240 --> 00:24:01,160
Intimate lovers being sweet with each other.

378
00:24:01,600 --> 00:24:03,040
You two got caught by me.

379
00:24:05,400 --> 00:24:07,040
Palace of Eternal Spring is busy.

380
00:24:07,040 --> 00:24:08,100
I'll get going now.

381
00:24:09,160 --> 00:24:09,920
Don't go!

382
00:24:10,080 --> 00:24:11,200
I'm just joking!

383
00:24:15,760 --> 00:24:16,720
Sorry, buddy.

384
00:24:17,400 --> 00:24:19,600
Who’d know that she couldn’t be teased?

385
00:24:20,400 --> 00:24:21,160
I’ll feed you.

386
00:24:21,160 --> 00:24:22,440
It's fine. You have me.

387
00:24:22,600 --> 00:24:23,480
Open your mouth.

388
00:24:23,480 --> 00:24:24,540
I'll do it on my own.

389
00:24:27,400 --> 00:24:29,720
It's hot.

390
00:24:33,800 --> 00:24:34,680
It hurts!

391
00:24:35,040 --> 00:24:35,970
Enough, enough.

392
00:24:37,440 --> 00:24:38,320
Let go!

393
00:24:41,320 --> 00:24:42,400
Fuca Fuheng,

394
00:24:43,800 --> 00:24:45,280
can I trust you?

395
00:24:51,880 --> 00:24:53,440
- Fourth Prince, stop messing around. - Here.

396
00:24:53,440 --> 00:24:54,800
- Fourth Prince. - Be good and take your medicine.

397
00:24:54,800 --> 00:24:55,660
Fourth Prince.

398
00:24:57,880 --> 00:24:58,740
Fourth Prince.

399
00:24:58,960 --> 00:25:00,620
What's wrong with Yongcheng?

400
00:25:01,360 --> 00:25:02,690
Imperial Consort Xian.

401
00:25:05,240 --> 00:25:08,170
Imperial Consort Xian, Fourth Prince caught a cold,

402
00:25:08,360 --> 00:25:09,920
but he refused to take in any of the medicine

403
00:25:09,920 --> 00:25:11,920
prescribed by the imperial doctor.

404
00:25:12,040 --> 00:25:14,440
A small child won't like taking medicines.

405
00:25:14,960 --> 00:25:15,720
Ask the imperial doctor

406
00:25:15,720 --> 00:25:17,920
if he can increase the dose of licorice,

407
00:25:18,240 --> 00:25:20,280
so that Fourth Prince will take it in.

408
00:25:20,280 --> 00:25:21,080
Quickly go.

409
00:25:21,400 --> 00:25:22,040
Yes.

410
00:25:27,000 --> 00:25:28,560
Yongcheng, what's wrong?

411
00:25:29,280 --> 00:25:30,810
I don't want you, bad woman!

412
00:25:30,840 --> 00:25:32,560
I want mother! I want mother!

413
00:25:32,560 --> 00:25:33,840
Imperial Consort Xian, please forgive him.

414
00:25:33,840 --> 00:25:36,080
Fourth Prince is young and insensible.

415
00:25:36,280 --> 00:25:37,560
If he offended you,

416
00:25:37,680 --> 00:25:39,640
I'm apologizing on his behalf.

417
00:25:39,840 --> 00:25:41,680
Prince is young, but you are not.

418
00:25:41,880 --> 00:25:42,880
What "bad woman"?

419
00:25:43,160 --> 00:25:44,690
Who taught him those words?

420
00:25:45,240 --> 00:25:46,370
Forget it, Zhen'er.

421
00:25:47,120 --> 00:25:48,280
It's just normal for a child this young

422
00:25:48,280 --> 00:25:50,160
to miss his mother.

423
00:25:50,520 --> 00:25:52,180
Don't make a fuss with a child.

424
00:25:52,280 --> 00:25:52,960
Empress!

425
00:25:52,960 --> 00:25:54,640
Yongcheng, Yongcheng!

426
00:25:56,600 --> 00:25:58,320
Yongcheng, Yongcheng!

427
00:25:58,600 --> 00:25:59,520
Mother’s here!

428
00:26:00,640 --> 00:26:02,120
Come, Yongcheng.

429
00:26:06,000 --> 00:26:06,720
Yongcheng,

430
00:26:07,480 --> 00:26:08,740
Yongcheng, look at me.

431
00:26:09,240 --> 00:26:09,880
My god,

432
00:26:10,840 --> 00:26:12,300
it's just a couple of days.

433
00:26:12,640 --> 00:26:14,440
How come you've gotten thinner?

434
00:26:15,520 --> 00:26:17,050
How did you take care of him?

435
00:26:17,200 --> 00:26:18,720
A prince is precious.

436
00:26:18,880 --> 00:26:20,410
How could you mistreat him?

437
00:26:21,200 --> 00:26:22,680
Consort, I dare not.

438
00:26:23,160 --> 00:26:25,160
I've been meticulously taking care of Fourth Prince

439
00:26:25,160 --> 00:26:26,480
and never slacked off.

440
00:26:26,480 --> 00:26:28,010
Meticulously taking care?

441
00:26:28,360 --> 00:26:29,090
Tell me then,

442
00:26:30,040 --> 00:26:32,300
how come the Prince has become like this?

443
00:26:32,640 --> 00:26:34,200
You can’t have taken care of him properly.

444
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:36,400
Consort Jia, what are you saying?

445
00:26:36,920 --> 00:26:39,000
Empress has been anxious and worried for Fourth Prince.

446
00:26:39,000 --> 00:26:40,520
We've successively invited imperial doctors to check him.

447
00:26:40,520 --> 00:26:41,720
What do you mean by not taking care of him properly?

448
00:26:41,720 --> 00:26:43,120
Yongcheng, don't worry.

449
00:26:44,280 --> 00:26:45,140
Mother’s here.

450
00:26:45,600 --> 00:26:46,520
Mother’s here,

451
00:26:47,040 --> 00:26:49,240
and no one would dare bully you anymore.

452
00:26:53,680 --> 00:26:54,840
I missed you so much.

453
00:26:55,320 --> 00:26:57,760
- Here. - Consort Jia is here to see Fourth Prince.

454
00:26:57,760 --> 00:26:58,800
Let’s go out.

455
00:27:00,320 --> 00:27:01,560
Let me look at you.

456
00:27:21,840 --> 00:27:23,960
Empress, Consort Jia has left.

457
00:27:26,760 --> 00:27:29,200
Obviously she was crying on purpose in front of you.

458
00:27:29,200 --> 00:27:29,960
Zhen'er.

459
00:27:30,560 --> 00:27:32,160
I didn't say anything wrong.

460
00:27:32,520 --> 00:27:34,280
Fourth Prince has just been here for half a month.

461
00:27:34,280 --> 00:27:36,480
She comes to cry here every two or three days

462
00:27:36,480 --> 00:27:38,080
and always makes such huge movements.

463
00:27:38,080 --> 00:27:39,740
People outside are gossiping

464
00:27:39,760 --> 00:27:42,020
that you're mistreating Fourth Prince.

465
00:27:42,560 --> 00:27:45,560
Consort Jia loves her son dearly and is just showing excessive concern.

466
00:27:45,560 --> 00:27:47,160
Nothing strange about that.

467
00:27:49,280 --> 00:27:51,480
It was His Majesty’s order

468
00:27:51,680 --> 00:27:53,520
that Fourth Prince stay in Palace of Receiving Celestial Favor.

469
00:27:53,520 --> 00:27:55,440
If she's so capable, she should go to His Majesty.

470
00:27:55,440 --> 00:27:57,160
Why must she keep making things hard on you?

471
00:27:57,160 --> 00:27:59,690
Because she knows you're kind and venerable!

472
00:27:59,800 --> 00:28:01,860
I don't care what Consort Jia thinks.

473
00:28:02,320 --> 00:28:04,050
Anyway, the child is innocent.

474
00:28:04,080 --> 00:28:05,610
Now that he's staying here,

475
00:28:06,000 --> 00:28:07,600
we must take good care of him.

476
00:28:08,280 --> 00:28:09,440
Yes, yes...

477
00:28:10,280 --> 00:28:12,140
you are always this kindhearted.

478
00:28:12,240 --> 00:28:13,760
I am the one who is petty.

479
00:28:15,400 --> 00:28:16,060
Yongcheng,

480
00:28:16,240 --> 00:28:16,760
come.

481
00:28:17,480 --> 00:28:19,080
Okay, we're not eating this.

482
00:28:20,240 --> 00:28:23,440
Where's the light porridge that I asked them to send here?

483
00:28:23,560 --> 00:28:25,080
Fourth Prince doesn't like to eat porridge.

484
00:28:25,080 --> 00:28:27,400
I ordered the kitchen to make some soup.

485
00:28:28,880 --> 00:28:29,610
Don't worry.

486
00:28:29,760 --> 00:28:32,160
The soup is made from rice and a little meat.

487
00:28:32,480 --> 00:28:34,760
Fourth Prince wouldn't take in even one mouthful of porridge.

488
00:28:34,760 --> 00:28:36,960
I am just afraid that he'll lack energy.

489
00:28:38,880 --> 00:28:39,800
I’ll do it.

490
00:28:44,920 --> 00:28:47,040
Yongcheng, be good and eat your soup.

491
00:28:48,360 --> 00:28:49,240
Yongcheng,

492
00:28:49,560 --> 00:28:50,880
if you eat your food,

493
00:28:51,080 --> 00:28:53,320
I'll let your mother visit you every day.

494
00:28:53,320 --> 00:28:54,040
Okay?

495
00:28:55,080 --> 00:28:57,010
Fourth Prince, don’t be like that.

496
00:28:57,360 --> 00:29:00,080
Not only your mother, but also your Royal Father.

497
00:29:00,080 --> 00:29:01,810
As long as you behave yourself,

498
00:29:02,080 --> 00:29:03,800
I'll ask him to come visit you.

499
00:29:36,280 --> 00:29:38,280
Empress, how about this hairpin?

500
00:29:40,200 --> 00:29:41,560
Fourth Prince is sick.

501
00:29:41,960 --> 00:29:43,560
I'm not in the mood to doll up.

502
00:29:44,040 --> 00:29:45,080
You decide it.

503
00:29:46,520 --> 00:29:47,440
Empress,

504
00:29:47,560 --> 00:29:49,560
you are being too kind.

505
00:29:49,720 --> 00:29:50,840
You are treating Fourth Prince so well,

506
00:29:50,840 --> 00:29:52,000
but others are misunderstanding it.

507
00:29:52,000 --> 00:29:53,480
I feel you’re wronged.

508
00:29:53,680 --> 00:29:54,360
Enough.

509
00:29:56,880 --> 00:29:58,880
Later, go to the Imperial Hospital.

510
00:29:59,400 --> 00:30:01,080
Ask Director Zhang of Imperial Hospital to come over and check his pulse.

511
00:30:01,080 --> 00:30:03,560
He is specialized in pediatrics.

512
00:30:04,080 --> 00:30:04,760
Yes.

513
00:30:04,840 --> 00:30:07,080
Empress, Empress, Empress!

514
00:30:07,280 --> 00:30:09,680
Fourth Prince, he... Please go have a look.

515
00:30:13,920 --> 00:30:14,720
Consort Xian,

516
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:17,480
Consort Xian,

517
00:30:18,040 --> 00:30:19,320
my child is this sick.

518
00:30:19,560 --> 00:30:21,000
You treat it as if nothing is wrong.

519
00:30:21,000 --> 00:30:22,560
Return me my healthy son!

520
00:30:22,560 --> 00:30:23,360
Return me!

521
00:30:23,360 --> 00:30:23,760
Consort!

522
00:30:23,760 --> 00:30:25,560
Consort Jia, what are you doing?

523
00:30:26,960 --> 00:30:28,760
Everyone here in the Palace says

524
00:30:29,240 --> 00:30:32,000
that you are kind, virtuous, noble and unsullied.

525
00:30:32,000 --> 00:30:33,560
But how were you taking care of him?

526
00:30:33,560 --> 00:30:34,760
Look at him yourself!

527
00:30:36,440 --> 00:30:39,320
Imperial Consort Xian, Fourth Prince is having a fever.

528
00:30:39,320 --> 00:30:40,440
It's so scary.

529
00:30:40,560 --> 00:30:42,080
Yongcheng is having a fever again?

530
00:30:42,080 --> 00:30:42,960
Let me see.

531
00:30:42,960 --> 00:30:44,080
Don't touch my son!

532
00:30:46,040 --> 00:30:47,520
What are you shouting about?

533
00:30:47,520 --> 00:30:49,320
Greetings to you, Your Majesty.

534
00:30:49,560 --> 00:30:51,020
Your Majesty, look at him.

535
00:30:59,040 --> 00:31:00,080
Go and invite Director Zhang of Imperial Hospital.

536
00:31:00,080 --> 00:31:00,880
Yes.

537
00:31:05,560 --> 00:31:07,680
Your Majesty, I wasn't able to take care of him properly,

538
00:31:07,680 --> 00:31:09,000
so Fourth Prince got sick.

539
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:11,260
I'm guilty. May Your Majesty forgive me.

540
00:31:11,520 --> 00:31:12,280
Empress,

541
00:31:12,760 --> 00:31:15,240
you guarded by Fourth Prince's side till midnight.

542
00:31:15,240 --> 00:31:16,840
Fourth Prince was well then.

543
00:31:17,080 --> 00:31:19,040
No one could have predicted the fever.

544
00:31:19,040 --> 00:31:20,400
How come it became your mistake?

545
00:31:20,400 --> 00:31:21,520
Zhen'er, shut up.

546
00:31:25,560 --> 00:31:26,360
Your Majesty,

547
00:31:27,520 --> 00:31:28,960
I made a mistake,

548
00:31:29,080 --> 00:31:31,080
and I shouldn't beg for your forgiveness.

549
00:31:31,080 --> 00:31:33,520
Even if you ask me to leave Yongcheng,

550
00:31:33,800 --> 00:31:35,530
I could only accept your order.

551
00:31:35,680 --> 00:31:36,960
But Imperial Consort Xian

552
00:31:36,960 --> 00:31:38,560
isn't the birth mother of Yongcheng.

553
00:31:38,560 --> 00:31:41,760
She doesn't have any experience in taking care of a child.

554
00:31:41,800 --> 00:31:43,640
Yongcheng has just been here for half a month

555
00:31:43,640 --> 00:31:45,170
and already got sick twice.

556
00:31:45,240 --> 00:31:47,000
I visited him early today

557
