would use my kindness

839
00:41:18,400 --> 00:41:20,040
to frame Consort Xian.

840
00:41:21,040 --> 00:41:22,280
A woman like that

841
00:41:22,520 --> 00:41:23,040
is indeed unworthy

842
00:41:23,040 --> 00:41:24,880
to be Yongcheng’s mother.

843
00:41:26,040 --> 00:41:26,880
But

844
00:41:27,200 --> 00:41:30,280
Yongcheng had been living in Palace of Gathered Elegance.

845
00:41:30,280 --> 00:41:32,010
After suddenly leaving there,

846
00:41:32,040 --> 00:41:34,300
he surely will feel very uncomfortable.

847
00:41:35,560 --> 00:41:37,160
In my opinion,

848
00:41:37,960 --> 00:41:38,880
maybe,

849
00:41:39,600 --> 00:41:40,760
you can let me

850
00:41:41,440 --> 00:41:44,300
take Yongcheng back to Palace of Gathered Elegance

851
00:41:44,320 --> 00:41:45,980
and I'll take good care of him.

852
00:41:46,520 --> 00:41:47,360
Or else,

853
00:41:47,720 --> 00:41:50,320
Consort Xian doesn't know how to raise a child.

854
00:41:50,720 --> 00:41:52,560
It almost led to trouble.

855
00:41:53,000 --> 00:41:53,920
Your Majesty,

856
00:41:54,920 --> 00:41:56,840
what do you think?

857
00:42:00,320 --> 00:42:01,650
Noble Consort Empress,

858
00:42:01,680 --> 00:42:04,120
Consort Xian indeed doesn't know how to take care of a child,

859
00:42:04,120 --> 00:42:05,720
but practice makes perfect.

860
00:42:06,080 --> 00:42:07,640
Her absolute sincerity towards the child

861
00:42:07,640 --> 00:42:09,970
can even compete that of his birth mother.

862
00:42:15,840 --> 00:42:16,800
Yongcheng

863
00:42:17,640 --> 00:42:19,640
will stay in Palace of Receiving Celestial Favor.

864
00:42:19,640 --> 00:42:20,480
I believe

865
00:42:20,960 --> 00:42:23,420
that Consort Xian will take good care of him.

866
00:42:24,120 --> 00:42:25,520
Thank you, Your Majesty.

867
00:42:34,960 --> 00:42:38,320
I've heard that Consort Chun is very knowledgeable

868
00:42:38,400 --> 00:42:40,060
and well-versed in medicine.

869
00:42:40,280 --> 00:42:41,640
Today,

870
00:42:41,640 --> 00:42:44,120
I've learned a lot.

871
00:42:44,960 --> 00:42:46,560
Thank you, Noble Consort Empress.

872
00:42:46,560 --> 00:42:49,080
I'm flattered.

